text: Ayshan Ahmadova (; born 5 May 2000) is an Azerbaijani footballer who plays as a defender for Kazakhstani Women's Championship club FC Okzhetpes and the Azerbaijan women's national team. ==References== Category:2000 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Azerbaijani women's footballers Category:Azerbaijan women's international footballers Category:FC Okzhetpes players Category:Azerbaijani expatriate footballers Category:Azerbaijani expatriate sportspeople in Kazakhstan Category:Expatriate women's footballers in Kazakhstan
